title.narrative: AgResults: Innovation in Research and Delivery External Impact Evaluation (Global)

description.narrative: AgResults is a new multilateral initiative seeking to enhance smallholder welfare and improve food security through the use of "pull" mechanisms. The scope of the external impact evaluation is to: 1) Define a compelling and coherent impact evaluation framework for the AgResults Initiative; 2) Design impact evaluations for 5-6 pilots; 3) Design, implement and analyze field surveys for 3 pilots; 4) Assist as needed in the communication of the learning agenda, impact evaluation strategy and evaluations results; and 5) Participate in steering committee meetings as and when required.;
